HOW TO INSTALL

link all.inc file from your shell script as this
( Keep an eye on the [space] character after dot ) :

. /usr/lib/sh/all.inc

Alternatively you can link only a file as this:

. /usr/lib/sh/common.inc	( This is mandatory for this way. )
. /usr/lib/sh/strings.inc	( This is the include file you prefer. )

Recommended path for .inc files is /usr/lib/sh/